hvariant="bold">A</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mrow><mml:mo>←</mml:mo><mml:mi mathvariant="bold">L</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:msubsup></mml:math></alternatives></inline-formula> and the non-cooperators <bold>C</bold><sup><bold>←L</bold></sup>. <bold>C</bold>: Mean time until respective generation time is reached. One generation corresponds to the biomass doubling time of the simulated community.</p>
