    <sec id="sec011">
      <title>Statistical analysis</title>
      <p>Statistical analysis was conducted with R 4.0.3 [<xref rid="pcbi.1009777.ref044" ref-type="bibr">44</xref>]. Plots were created with the package ‘ggplot2’ [<xref rid="pcbi.1009777.ref045" ref-type="bibr">45</xref>]. R-scripts are provided in <xref rid="pcbi.1009777.s004" ref-type="supplementary-material">S1 Scripts</xref>.</p>
